TITLE: Implementing a Timer with Status Bar Updates in Obsidian Plugin
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows how to create a status bar clock that updates every second using registerInterval with window.setInterval(). It properly handles interval cleanup when the plugin unloads and demonstrates updating UI elements periodically.
SOURCE: https://github.com/obsidianmd/obsidian-developer-docs/blob/main/en/Plugins/Events.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

