SOURCE: https://github.com/obsidianmd/obsidian-developer-docs/blob/main/en/Plugins/User interface/Commands.md#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
this.addCommand({
  id: 'example-command',
  name: 'Example command',
  checkCallback: (checking: boolean) => {
    const value = getRequiredValue();

    if (value) {
      if (!checking) {
        doCommand(value);
      }

      return true
    }

    return false;
  },
});
```

