SOURCE: https://github.com/obsidianmd/obsidian-developer-docs/blob/main/en/Plugins/Releasing/Plugin guidelines.md#2025-04-21_snippet_17

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
function test(): Promise<string | null> {
  return requestUrl('https://example.com')
    .then(res => res.text
    .catch(e => {
      console.log(e);
      return null;
    });
}
```
